"in verschiedenen Ansichten."

#: app/html/menus/dashboard/tabs/changelog.php:655
msgid "Fixed certain issues with required attributes in listings editors."
msgstr ""
"Bestimmte Probleme mit erforderlichen Attributen in Listing-Editoren wurden "
"behoben."

#: app/html/menus/dashboard/tabs/changelog.php:661
msgid ""
"[PRO] Introduced authentication features including login, registration, and "
